{"_id":"class-monk","name":"Monk","type":"class","img":"icons/svg/sword.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Monks are disciplined warriors who rely on unarmed strikes, speed, and mental focus. They do not use armor or shields; their AC bonus and fast movement apply only when unarmored and unencumbered.</p><h3>Alignment</h3><p>Any lawful.</p><h3>Key Class Features</h3><ul><li><strong>Unarmed Strike:</strong> Improved Unarmed Strike as bonus feat; increased unarmed damage by level; can deal lethal or nonlethal.</li><li><strong>Flurry of Blows:</strong> When unarmored, make one extra attack at highest BAB with a penalty (lessens by 5th and 9th); greater flurry at 11th adds a second extra attack.</li><li><strong>AC Bonus:</strong> When unarmored and unencumbered, add Wisdom bonus to AC; +1 at 5th level and every 5 levels thereafter.</li><li><strong>Evasion (2nd), Fast Movement (3rd), Still Mind (3rd), Ki Strike (4th/10th/16th), Slow Fall (4th), Purity of Body (5th), Wholeness of Body (7th), Diamond Body (11th), Abundant Step (12th), Diamond Soul (13th), Quivering Palm (15th), Empty Body (19th), Perfect Self (20th).</strong></li></ul><p><em>Ex-monks:</em> A monk who becomes nonlawful cannot gain new monk levels. A monk who gains a level in another class can never again raise monk level.</p>","hitDie":"d8","babProgression":"average","saves":{"fort":"good","ref":"good","will":"good"},"skillPointsPerLevel":4,"classSkills":[{"key":"balance","name":"Balance"},{"key":"climb","name":"Climb"},{"key":"craft-alchemy","name":"Craft (Alchemy)"},{"key":"craft-armorsmithing","name":"Craft (Armorsmithing)"},{"key":"craft-bowmaking","name":"Craft (Bowmaking)"},{"key":"craft-weaponsmithing","name":"Craft (Weaponsmithing)"},{"key":"craft-trapmaking","name":"Craft (Trapsmithing)"},{"key":"escapeArtist","name":"Escape Artist"},{"key":"hide","name":"Hide"},{"key":"jump","name":"Jump"},{"key":"knowledge-arcana","name":"Knowledge (Arcana)"},{"key":"knowledge-religion","name":"Knowledge (Religion)